lv = LV.from_pyvista_read("../sample_files/lvtetmesh.vtk") # load reference mesh (can also be done from other methods)
lv.tetrahedralize(backend=TETRA_BACKEND.WILDMESHING, stop_quality=1000)
lv.plot(show_edges=True)
